SA-CONF
Identification of structurally conserved and flexible regions of a protein.
 __________________________________________________________________________________
|__________________________________________________________________________________|

Leslie Regad, Jean-Baptiste Cheron, Caroline Senac, Dhoha Triki, Delphine Flatters, Anne-Claude Camproux
 __________________________________________________________________________________
|__________________________________________________________________________________|

** HOW TO RUN

1 ) Requirements
    - python 3
        -- Packages: python-dev python-biopython 
    - clustalw / tcoffee

2 ) Instructions
    run saconf.x64 or saconf.x32 for your own architecture.
    - Arguments:
    usage: saconf_LR.py [-h] -i IDFILE [-m METHOD] [-p PDBPATH] [-a ALIGNFILE]
                    [-o OUTPUT] [-u UNIPROT]
    argument -i/--IDfile is required
